# This is instruction of manualy installing

1) Installing of the dependencies:
    * Arch-based linux:
        $ sudo pacman -S gcc make boost

    * Ubuntu-based linux:
        $ sudo apt install gcc make libboost-all-dev
    
    * Termux (linux terminal emulation on android):
        $ pkg install clang make boost

2) Building an executable file:
    $ make && make clean

3) Start program:
    $ ./fcryptor
